{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_bg.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_21.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_21.png","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_22.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}]},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_110.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day22.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime02","chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Say, Mom...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What is it, Mabayu?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You can see the future, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Sure, if I'm feeling up to it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's so cool!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yep, it's a gift I've been blessed with."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And because of that gift,@I can help everyone."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_111.exp3.json","id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I might be in trouble though,@if I ever lost it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So what happens if you change the future?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_114.exp3.json","id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm, I'm afraid the future can't be changed."},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Why?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, now that's a good question.@I don't even know the answer."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But it won't change,@no matter how hard you try."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Maybe it's because fate is already@decided from the beginning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-15"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But you're telling fortunes, aren't you?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What do you do if you see@a bad future you can't change?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Telling someone would only@make them feel bad, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes, that's true."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So in times like that, I just@keep it to myself, deep inside."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Deep inside...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll only tell them good things.@That way, we'll both be happy."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Doesn't it hurt?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-23"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If your heart is full of bad stuff@you can't talk to anyone about..."},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...then I think it'd start to hurt."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp3.json","id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Holding onto someone's future@can be a painful responsibility."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So it gets tough sometimes."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_114.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But...I take pride in what I do."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The gift of seeing the future@is my very life."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-30"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your life...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_111.exp3.json","id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-31"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I appreciate your concern though."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-32"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm lucky to have a sweet daughter@like you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801201}],"textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":833400,"pos":1}]},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime22","chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-34"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Huh...?","textAvColorRGB":"255255255"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp3.json","id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-35"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]It can't be..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":833400,"pos":2}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Mom?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-37"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-38"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom, what's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-39"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Please, stay away!"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-40"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What..?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-41"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I saw it..."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-42"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I saw it!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_23161.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp3.json","id":200911,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"deleteArmatureList":[1],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day22.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":0.2,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":200911,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-43"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","surround":"8036_futon","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]...!!!","textAvColor":"textMabayu","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.01},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":200911,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-44"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]*Pant* *Pant*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200911,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-45"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Was that...a dream...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200911,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-46"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200911}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200901,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-47"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]...No, that's not it."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-48"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]A memory..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104204/vo_full_905122-005-49"}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]A memory of...Mom..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
